ет, а матери, которую звали Maude Bokeshull, 19. Он женился на женщине по имени Maud Francis перед 2 ноябрь 1381 г. в местности миддлесекс, Англия. У них был по крайней мере 1 сын. Он умер 2 ноября 1381 г. в местности Лондон, Англия в возрасте 59 лет и был похоронен в местности сити оф лондон, Англия, Великобритания."},"sm":{"about 1323–2 November 1381":"e tusa o le 1323–2 Novema 1381","1323–1381":"1323–1381","1362–1424":"1362–1424","1382–1424":"1382–1424","1351–1420":"1351–1420","1352–1416":"1352–1416","1295–1325":"1295–1325","1305–1326":"1305–1326","2 November 1381":"2 Novema 1381","1352":"1352","18 July 1326":"18 Iulai 1326","1351":"1351","1362":"1362","1295":"1295","1382":"1382","before 2 November 1381":"a'e le'I oo le 2 Novema 1381","1381":"1381","1305":"1305","1337":"1337","1326":"1326","1325":"1325","1424":"1424","1323":"1323","1453":"1453","1420":"1420","about 1323":"e tusa o le 1323","1328":"1328","1416":"1416","Cockermouth, Cumberland, England":"Cockermouth, Cumberland, Egelani","Middlesex, England":"Middlesex, Egelani","Sussex, England":"Sussex, Egelani","London, England":"London, Egelani","Jesus' Chapel, Old St. Paul's, London, Middlesex,England":"City of London, Egelani, United Kingdom","Dorset, England":"Dorset, Egelani"},"sk":{"about 1323–2 November 1381":"okolo 1323–2. november 1381","1323–1381":"1323–1381","1362–1424":"1362–1424","1382–1424":"1382–1424","1351–1420":"1351–1420","1352–1416":"1352–1416","1295–1325":"1295–1325","1305–1326":"1305–1326","2 November 1381":"2. november 1381","1352":"1352","18 July 1326":"18. júl 1326","1351":"1351","1362":"1362","1295":"1295","1382":"1382","before 2 November 1381":"pred rokom 2. november 1381","1381":"1381","1305":"1305","1337":"1337","1326":"1326","1325":"1325","1424":"1424","1323":"1323","1453":"1453","1420":"1420","about 1323":"okolo 1323","1328":"1328","1416":"1416","Cockermouth, Cumberland, England":"Cockermouth, Cumberland, England","Middlesex, England":"Middlesex, England","Sussex, England":"Sussex, 